item.title: Differences are Strengths with Jen Kirkley
item.description:
Today on the podcast, we are joined by children’s book author Jen Kirkley! Jen joins the podcast to discuss her debut book, William DoGooder and the Trail of Friends, which showcases to children that their differences are their strengths. 

About the Guest:

Jen Kirkley is a wife and mother of four who works as a physician assistant in cardiothoracic surgery. She lives in Louisiana with her family in a house they have enjoyed renovating over the past ten years... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/chaos-and-cookies/
